<title>USA: LG&amp;E holders to vote Oct 14 on KU merger.</title>
<headline>LG&amp;E holders to vote Oct 14 on KU merger.</headline>
<dateline>LOUISVILLE, Ky. 1997-07-31</dateline>
<text>
<p>Energy services company LG&amp;E Energy Corp said Thursday it would hold a special shareholder meeting on October 14 to vote on the proposed merger with KU Energy Corp.</p>
<p>KU Energy will also hold a special shareholder meeting on that date, the company said.</p>
<p>The record date for both meetings is August 8.</p>
<p>KU and LG&amp;E said in May they would merge in a deal then valued at about $1.54 billion.</p>
<p>((Wall Street desk 212-859-1730))</p>
